s. Obviously it would be preferable, for Voyager=E2=80=99s customers, if so=
meone just=C2=A0bought=C2=A0Voyager for, you know, $1 plus a promise to mak=
e customers whole. (That is more or less  what happened to BlockFi Inc. las=
t week: FTX US, Sam Bankman-Fried=E2=80=99s crypto exchange, bought it for =
a small amount of money plus a larger credit facility that is subordinated =
to customer funds.)But nobody has offered to buy Voyager and make customers=
