ial or full ownership of the reorganized Company.=C2=A0Yeah you know anythi=
ng=E2=80=99s possible.=C2=A0A few other points. Alameda Research Ltd., Sam =
Bankman-Fried=E2=80=99s crypto hedge fund, is all over this case. It is Voy=
ager=E2=80=99s second-largest=C2=A0debtor, owing $376.8 million to Voyager.=
