in isn=E2=80=99t worth $40,000. Giving you the $40,000 would dramatically r=
educe the recovery for the rest of Voyager=E2=80=99s customers. So it=E2=80=
=99s asking the bankruptcy court to stop these chargebacks[5]:ACH transacti=
ons, while critical to the Debtors=E2=80=99 flow of funds, also leave the D=
ebtors susceptible to fraudulent chargebacks by customers of the MC FBO Acc=
ount (the =E2=80=9CACH Chargeback=E2=80=9D). This occurs when customers uti=
