: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; bord=
er-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #cc=
c;">filed for Chapter 11 bankruptcy</a> in New York and, while it doesn=E2=
=80=99t have enough money to pay back its customers, it=C2=A0<em>does=C2=A0=
</em>have some tokens to give them. From Voyager=E2=80=99s=C2=A0<a href=3D"=
https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/28287506.259574/aHR0cHM6Ly93d=
3cucHJuZXdzd2lyZS5jb20vbmV3cy1yZWxlYXNlcy92b3lhZ2VyLWRpZ2l0YWwtY29tbWVuY2Vz=
