arget=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !important;=
 border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-styl=
e: solid; background-color: #ccc;">released some financial data as of June =
30</a>, showing at least $2.3 billion of assets, of which about $650 millio=
n is loans to Three Arrows; if everything else is money-good then customers=
 should get back=C2=A072 cents on the dollar, though hoo boy is that not in=
vestment advice.[1])=C2=A0And to make it up to you, you will also get:</p><=
ol style=3D"list-style-type: decimal; padding-left: 40px; margin: 16px 0;">=
=09<li style=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">Shares of stock in what=E2=80=99s left=
 of Voyager, giving you the upside in its future business.</li>=09<li style=
