=80=99s loyalty and rewards program.=E2=80=9D If you own Voyager tokens you=
 can use them to =E2=80=9Cearn a variety of rewards and incentives, includi=
ng higher referral bonuses, lower=C2=A0transaction fees, prioritized custom=
er support, higher PIK Interest rates, and access to special events and inv=
estment opportunities.=E2=80=9D Imagine! Imagine earning that referral bonu=
s. Imagine calling your uncle to be like =E2=80=9Chey I have all these loya=
lty tokens from a crypto exchange that just went bankrupt and lost my Bitco=
in, you should sign up.=E2=80=9D=C2=A0</li>=09<li style=3D"margin-bottom: 5=
px;">A share of Voyager=E2=80=99s claim against Three Arrows, which is <a h=
