reversible, immutable blockchains, code is law, etc., but if your bank move=
s dollars out of your=C2=A0bank account you can try=C2=A0calling them up an=
d asking them to reverse the transfer for fraud.=C2=A0</p><p style=3D"margi=
n: 16px 0;">The problem for Voyager is that customers sent it a bunch of mo=
