provide that the business of the Surviving Corporation is conducted in a ma=
nner that preserves and enhances the Essential Integrity of the Brand. As p=
art of this responsibility, the Company Board may prevent any action by<br =
/>the CEO in the areas of new product introduction, the changing of product=
