erials and the licensing or other use of the Ben &amp; Jerry=E2=80=99s trad=
emark that, in each case, a majority of the Company Board reasonably determ=
ines to be inconsistent with the Essential Integrity of the Brand.</p></blo=
ckquote><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">And the board gets to more or less app=
oint itself: The majority of directors are =E2=80=9CClass I Directors,=E2=
